<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1910-05-07T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1910-05-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="608" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d608">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Her Majesty Queen <persName type="from">Alexandra</persName> to President <persName type="to">Taft</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-05-07"><hi rend="italic">May 7,
                                1910</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>I am deeply touched by your telegram, and I ask you to convey my
                            heartfelt thanks to the people and the Government of the United States
                            for their sympathy in my irreparable loss and sorrow.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Alexandra</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>